trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for selecting and editing an expressions binding collection at design time.

An instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor> class is a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor> object that can be used at design time to select and edit a collection of expression bindings, and assign the expressions to a control property.
trans-unit.target: Una instancia de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor> clase es un <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor> objeto que puede utilizarse en tiempo de diseño para seleccionar y editar una colección de enlaces de expresión y asigna las expresiones a una propiedad de control.

trans-unit.source: A designer host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], uses the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> class implementations with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionConverter> classes to set the expression bindings for control properties at design time, and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlPersister> class to persist the expressions for run time.
trans-unit.target: Host un diseñador, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], usa el <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder> y <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> clase implementaciones con el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor> y <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionConverter> clases para definir los enlaces de expresión para las propiedades de control en tiempo de diseño y la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlPersister> clase conservar las expresiones de tiempo de ejecución.

trans-unit.source: Expression strings reference a localizable resource, an application setting, a connection string, or a custom expression type.
trans-unit.target: Las cadenas de expresión hacen referencia a un recurso localizable, una configuración de aplicación, una cadena de conexión o un tipo de expresión personalizada.

trans-unit.source: The expression string is bound to the control property at design time, and then used at run time to determine the value for the property.
trans-unit.target: La cadena de expresión se enlaza a la propiedad de control en tiempo de diseño y, a continuación, se utiliza en tiempo de ejecución para determinar el valor de la propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor" /> class.
An <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext" /> object that can be used to gain additional context information such as the associated control.
A service provider object through which editing services can be obtained.
An instance of the object being edited.
Edits the value of the specified object with the specified service provider and context.
An <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> object containing the selected expressions; otherwise, if no expressions are selected, the <paramref name="value" /> object.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> method launches the user interface for editing the `value` object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> método inicia la interfaz de usuario para editar la `value` objeto.

trans-unit.source: The designer host calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> method when you attempt to edit the value of a property that this editor is associated with.
trans-unit.target: El host del diseñador llama el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> método cuando se intenta editar el valor de una propiedad que está asociado este editor.

trans-unit.source: The input service provider is used to obtain any editing services that are required within the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A>.
trans-unit.target: El proveedor de servicios de entrada se utiliza para obtener los servicios de edición que se deben incluir en el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A>.

trans-unit.source: A designer host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], uses the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> class implementations with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionConverter> classes to set the expression bindings for control properties at design time, and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlPersister> class to persist the expressions for run time.
trans-unit.target: Host un diseñador, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], usa el <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder> y <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> clase implementaciones con el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor> y <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionConverter> clases para definir los enlaces de expresión para las propiedades de control en tiempo de diseño y la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlPersister> clase conservar las expresiones de tiempo de ejecución.

trans-unit.source: Expression strings reference a localizable resource, an application setting, a connection string, or a custom expression type.
trans-unit.target: Las cadenas de expresión hacen referencia a un recurso localizable, una configuración de aplicación, una cadena de conexión o un tipo de expresión personalizada.

trans-unit.source: The expression string is bound to the control property at design time, and then used at run time to determine the value for the property.
trans-unit.target: La cadena de expresión se enlaza a la propiedad de control en tiempo de diseño y, a continuación, se utiliza en tiempo de ejecución para determinar el valor de la propiedad.

trans-unit.source: If users cancel the user interface without modifying the expression binding collection, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> method returns the input `value` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Si los usuarios cancelan la interfaz de usuario sin modificar la expresión de enlace de la colección, el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> método devuelve la entrada `value` parámetro.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext" /> object that can be used to gain additional context information.
Gets the editing style that is associated with this editor for the specified context.
An <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle" /> enumeration value indicating the editing style for the provided user interface.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> method returns the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle.Modal> value by default.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> método devuelve el <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle.Modal> valor de forma predeterminada.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> is not supported in the specified context, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> returns <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle.None>.
trans-unit.target: Si <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> no se admite en el contexto especificado, el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionsCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> devuelve <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle.None>.
